{"tid":520900,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"星期六日裝修 擾人假日安寧👎🏻 橙自私","createTime":"2018-01-06T02:27:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-06T02:52:51.000Z","uid":133629,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5493ec1b93981ed254afad10ac37253243e4d4ef","tid":520900,"uid":133629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T02:27:50.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲打覺得有人星期六（半日）、日重係度轉牆裝修真係好擾人？ <br />\n<br />\n星期一至五翻工OT都已經好chur。我只不過想係星期六日有翻d 時間係屋企休息下姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你有冇咁趕要係星期六日都係到轉牆呢？<br />\n<br />\n噪音管制條例都話假日（包星期日）唔可以制造撞擊式噪音<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁你係咪犯左法？<br />\n<br />\n我唔會怪裝修工人。要怪就怪做管理，做業主既管理不善。<br />\n<br />\n我就知我樓下有個咁既業主，聽講重係行會召集人。係呀，講緊你呀，姓橙，叫自私個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n比翻個安靜既假日小妹我，okay?"},{"pid":"f1b992a9f69297058f4fbac29523988f989d500b","tid":520900,"uid":65587,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T02:28:50.000Z","msg":"唔好係到單單打打我"},{"pid":"dec4915a4ed465da084aa0649b5463b789954979","tid":520900,"uid":25108,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T02:52:51.000Z","msg":"無記錯既話星期日係唔可以裝修<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.epd.gov.hk/epd/noise_education/web/CHI_EPD_HTML/m3/ordinance_7.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.epd.gov.hk%2Fepd%2Fnoise_education%2Fweb%2FCHI_EPD_HTML%2Fm3%2Fordinance_7.html&d=OozWam4SwW%2B8H43GDGsGh0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=f3fcecc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.epd.gov.hk/epd/noise_education/web/CHI_EPD_HTML/m3/ordinance_7.html</a>"}]}